Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Linabuan Sur Elementary School in the Municipality of Banga, Province of Aklan, to Don Josue Songcuya Memorial Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 733
An Act Changing the Name of the Linabuan Sur Elementary School in the Municipality of Banga, Province of Aklan, to Don Josue Songcuya Memorial Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Linabuan Sur Elementary School located in Barangay Linabuan Sur in the Municipality of Banga, Province of Aklan, is hereby changed to Don Josue Songcuya Memorial Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
